{
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "description": "Synthetic cross-client conformance cases for canonical forum content and fail-closed rendering.",
  "cases": [
    {
      "id": "plain-markup-remains-literal",
      "format": "plain_v1",
      "source": "**不是粗体**\n<script>alert('plain')</script>\n[危险](javascript:alert(1))\n![远程](https://tracker.example/pixel.png)",
      "canonical": { "accepted": true, "assetIds": [] },
      "render": {
        "containsText": ["**不是粗体**", "<script>alert('plain')</script>", "javascript:alert(1)"],
        "selectorCounts": { "strong": 0, "script": 0, "a": 0, "img": 0 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "markdown-gfm-and-safe-links",
      "format": "markdown_v1",
      "source": "# 规范标题\n\n**粗体** 与 ~~删除线~~\n\n- [x] 已完成\n\n| 列一 | 列二 |\n| --- | --- |\n| A | B |\n\n[站内](/forum/threads/1) [外链](https://example.com/path)",
      "canonical": { "accepted": true, "assetIds": [] },
      "render": {
        "containsText": ["规范标题", "粗体", "删除线", "已完成", "站内", "外链"],
        "selectorCounts": {
          "h2": 1,
          "strong": 1,
          "del": 1,
          "table": 1,
          "input[type='checkbox']": 1,
          "a[href='/forum/threads/1']": 1,
          "a[href='https://example.com/path'][target='_blank'][rel='noopener noreferrer nofollow ugc']": 1
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "markdown-raw-html-is-rejected-and-skipped",
      "format": "markdown_v1",
      "source": "<script>window.evil=1</script><iframe src=\"https://evil.example\"></iframe>\n\n安全文本",
      "canonical": { "accepted": false, "assetIds": [] },
      "render": {
        "containsText": ["安全文本"],
        "excludesText": ["window.evil=1"],
        "selectorCounts": { "script": 0, "iframe": 0 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "markdown-javascript-link-has-no-target",
      "format": "markdown_v1",
      "source": "[危险链接](javascript:alert(1))",
      "canonical": { "accepted": false, "assetIds": [] },
      "render": {
        "containsText": ["危险链接"],
        "selectorCounts": { "a": 1, "a[href]": 0 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "markdown-data-link-has-no-target",
      "format": "markdown_v1",
      "source": "[数据链接](data:text/html;base64,PHNjcmlwdD4=)",
      "canonical": { "accepted": false, "assetIds": [] },
      "render": {
        "containsText": ["数据链接"],
        "selectorCounts": { "a": 1, "a[href]": 0 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "markdown-remote-image-never-loads",
      "format": "markdown_v1",
      "source": "![跟踪像素](https://tracker.example/pixel.png)",
      "canonical": { "accepted": false, "assetIds": [] },
      "render": {
        "containsText": ["图片当前不可用：跟踪像素"],
        "selectorCounts": { "[role='img']": 1, "img": 0 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "markdown-data-image-never-loads",
      "format": "markdown_v1",
      "source": "![内联图片](data:image/png;base64,AAAA)",
      "canonical": { "accepted": false, "assetIds": [] },
      "render": {
        "containsText": ["图片当前不可用：内联图片"],
        "selectorCounts": { "[role='img']": 1, "img": 0 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "markdown-platform-image-uses-derived-delivery",
      "format": "markdown_v1",
      "source": "![校园风景](yourtj-asset:42)",
      "canonical": { "accepted": true, "assetIds": [42] },
      "render": {
        "containsText": [],
        "selectorCounts": {
          "img[src='https://cdn.example.test/asset-42.webp']": 1,
          "img[src^='yourtj-asset:']": 0
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "markdown-noncanonical-asset-id-fails-closed",
      "format": "markdown_v1",
      "source": "![畸形资源](yourtj-asset:042)",
      "canonical": { "accepted": false, "assetIds": [] },
      "render": {
        "containsText": ["图片当前不可用：畸形资源"],
        "selectorCounts": { "[role='img']": 1, "img": 0 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "markdown-malformed-link-remains-text",
      "format": "markdown_v1",
      "source": "[未闭合](javascript:alert(1)",
      "canonical": { "accepted": true, "assetIds": [] },
      "render": {
        "containsText": ["[未闭合](javascript:alert(1)"],
        "selectorCounts": { "a": 0 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "markdown-overlong-source-is-not-canonical",
      "format": "markdown_v1",
      "source": "界",
      "repeat": 50001,
      "canonical": { "accepted": false, "assetIds": [] },
      "render": {
        "containsText": ["界界界"],
        "textLength": 50001,
        "selectorCounts": { "p": 1 }
      }
    }
  ]
}
